						<b>Baek-Kimchi (white Kimchi)</b><br><br>
						Baek-Kimchi is favored in cold, northern province as winter storage foods. It is a quality Kimchi with various toppings that is not too salty or spicy. Its juice can be slightly frozen to give cold and fresh taste.<br><br>
						Baek-Kimchi is also well liked by foreigners. During the time for preparing Kimchi for the winter, it is favored in Seoul, Gyonggi-do, and central provinces.</td>
